ygData.subject: Brass
ygData.msgSnippet: Don t think brass is nerfed. I sat on the dock at Kaladim  & played my only brass song while waiting for boat to Freeport & again on the Siren s Bane. Went up
ygData.messageBody:
Don't think brass is nerfed. I sat on the dock at Kaladim & played my only brass song while waiting for boat to Freeport & again on the Siren's Bane. Went up from 20 to 40 in XP. So I guess it's a matter of finding a place that you can play disonance songs without getting hit on.

Jovvi Songangel
Bard of 20 songs
Drinal
